name: hudson-river-sub-bottom-profile-lines-r09272010
notes: Subbottom Profiler Tracklines. Data was collected November 5 to December 15, 2009, in the estuary north from Saugerties to Troy. Fugro utilized the GeoAcoustics GeoSwath and the EdgeTech SB216 Chirp subbottom profiler system for data collection. The sub-bottom trackplot was generated in ArcGIS from the GPS positions recorded in the Seg-Y file header.
